### List company areas
GET {{baseUrl}}/company_areas
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Create company area
POST {{baseUrl}}/company_areas
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "company_id": 1,
  "area": "South-West",
  "region": "SW",
  "description": "South region area",
  "active": true
}

### Get company area by id
GET {{baseUrl}}/company_areas/2
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Update company area
PUT {{baseUrl}}/company_areas/2
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "area": "North-East",
  "region": "NE",
  "description": "Updated description",
  "active": true
}

### Delete company area
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/company_areas/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
